{"tid":912204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輕熟女包浴巾控遭性侵　內心不願但沒反抗！男獲不起訴","createTime":"2018-11-22T13:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T14:11:59.000Z","uid":84436,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"164e3944badcf9f457f2b296979a1185d7c5cc26","tid":912204,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181121/1470238/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470238%2F&d=mrqfO2acVYv3V1DatE9AOV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9741e047\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470238%2F&h=fdc9688e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181121/1470238/</a><br />\n<br />\n1對男女上摩鐵，事後女方控男子性侵，但偵訊時，女子又說，性交時未反抗，但內心是不願意的，檢方認為，她與遭性侵的被害者反應不同，身體也未有傷，因此不起訴男子。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，1名桃園游姓男子（26歲）因工作結識大他7歲的女子，今年6月相約吃宵夜，時間晚了同意上摩鐵；女子事後控訴游男性侵，游男喊冤稱是「你情我願」，對方裸身圍著浴巾出來就自然發生關係。檢方調查，該女子事後說，性交時自己內心很不願意，但也沒講什麼話或反抗，游男沒有用強暴、脅迫手段逼她，也替游男口交、自己打開雙腳。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官認為，若女子遭性侵，當時單獨離開時，她卻未向櫃台報警，加上沒有明顯傷勢的驗傷報告，當下究竟是半推半就下，抑或已表強烈反抗仍遭性侵，仍有疑慮，因此游男不起訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"30fe268c660ef5d69a5cd4833e43bfa4c08db51a","tid":912204,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:11:07.000Z","msg":"遲啲簽埋性交同意書都會話內心其實不願意簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12a6b143199ad4378b8478eed90f12a1ec11d18","tid":912204,"uid":137569,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"164e3944badcf9f457f2b296979a1185d7c5cc26","tid":912204,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181121/1470238/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470238%2F&d=mrqfO2acVYv3V1DatE9AOV0